Extract pfp object from pfc, the paths of each flow from root to terminal node.

pf_path.Rd

Extract pfp object from pfc, the paths of each flow from root to terminal node.

Usage

pf_path(x)

Arguments

x

A pfc object

Value

A pfp object

pf_path(rpfc(100))
